Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Partying is\Nweakness for the soul, my friend, so I try and avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have given every\Nsingle thing, every ounce of my life to this craft,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to perfecting my\Ncraft, and I continue to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In the process, I\Nhave lost my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To regular\Nsociety, to people who wake up at 9 a.m.,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,who clock out at 5\Np.m.,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,they would look at\Nme and say, I've lost my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But me, I have\Nfound it almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Conor\NMcGregor. I'm a professional MMA fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is to be\Nworld lightweight champion in the UFC.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is to be\Nnumber one.
